                    "image": "Sidebar_2_AdditionalLore.png"
                },
                "html": "Regardless of their original ancestry, devourers are always Large\u2014fully 10 feet tall\u2014as the remains of their mortal form strain to contain the evil within. However, their withered and hollowed-out bodies rarely weigh more than a mere 200 pounds."
            },
