                "html": "The fact that devourers consume souls makes them particularly hated by the church of <a aonid=\"14\" game-obj=\"Deities\">Pharasma</a> and <a aonid=\"83\" game-obj=\"MonsterFamilies\">psychopomps</a> alike."
